      • clone

        public Object clone()
             throws CloneNotSupportedException
        Support cloning as for many Anys but just return this. We don't want unregulated creation of these objects since you can't compare them using normal equals() since that is always true! For those occasions when testing whether an object is AnyNull you have to compare by object identity.
